<https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/ministry-of-justice> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "The Ministry of Justice is a major government department, at the heart of the justice system. We work to protect and advance the principles of justice. Our vision is to deliver a world-class justice system that works for everyone in society. MOJ is a ministerial department, supported by 35 agencies and public bodies ."@en .
